{"tid":2076073,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想問咁係咪有d咩暗病","createTime":"2020-06-23T09:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T17:54:11.000Z","uid":334904,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"08cb7bab1e1c9828139831ffd931f079a27f5945","tid":2076073,"uid":334904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:12:54.000Z","msg":"我同朋友啱啱踩左一個鐘單車<br />\n到左小食亭我地坐底食d野<br />\n我買完野食番黎見到佢坐喺度中下中下<br />\n之後仲向後中就黎跌落地咁<br />\n我即刻扶住佢 <br />\n佢當時全程對眼都係睜得好大<br />\n我好驚不斷大嗌問佢做咩事<br />\n佢就um um沉沉唔知講乜 個樣好似霍金咁<br />\n我抱坐番直後佢冇幾耐清醒番<br />\n歴時二十秒左右<br />\n我嚇到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以為佢要死<br />\n佢清醒後堅持自己係眼瞓 仲話自己發左個夢<br />\n但我覺得冇可能 佢全程對眼都睜得好大<br />\n我好擔心 有冇大師知道會唔會有咩暗病"},{"pid":"fb16b41c0d9a6e840f0f3cc7fe3c52d20a84dd1d","tid":2076073,"uid":201056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27985498b58b069440059f82b0ebbefe21dfed24","tid":2076073,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:47:36.000Z","msg":"渴睡症？"},{"pid":"40f33dbd812fda5dd01d5cbceae2dd4d231912ab","tid":2076073,"uid":334904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb16b41c0d9a6e840f0f3cc7fe3c52d20a84dd1d","tid":2076073,"uid":201056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T09:16:05.000Z","msg":"Cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/